{"type":"article","id":16441,"title":"分享一些知乎右狗的答案","uid":31715,"topics":[216,1666],"contents":"可能答主本身不是右狗，但是答案本身体现右狗的风格，反苏反康米，下面还有些答案是姨粉写的。<br>\n1.过于姨学，深刻体现sm学的道理<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/jEYXsQK.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jEYXsQK.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/jEYXsQK.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n2.批判了左人所谓的历史决定论的逻辑<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/COiztaT.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/COiztaT.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/COiztaT.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n3.批判了左人关于资本主义周期性危机的看法<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/s7KO57g.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/s7KO57g.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/s7KO57g.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n4.姨粉的答案，用姨学批判了中国的传统文化<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/W8K3fWd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W8K3fWd.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/W8K3fWd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iuc2zth.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iuc2zth.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iuc2zth.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n5.和我的观点类似，知乎乃至大陆网络的川粉，多半是粉红，自干五乃至皇汉。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/KlRI5zO.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KlRI5zO.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/KlRI5zO.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n6.对左派右派的看法非常辛辣<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/luWCtCn.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/luWCtCn.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/luWCtCn.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n7.嘲讽了康米小鬼，指出康米多半没有好下场。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/YFwJW7p.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YFwJW7p.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/YFwJW7p.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-03-20","agreeCount":7,"discussionCount":0}